---
import Contact from "./Contact.astro";
---
<section class="pb-16 pt-2 sm:pb-20 sm:pt-6">
  <p class="mb-6 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-ink-3">
    Co-founder, Auxerta / California
  </p>

  <h1 class="font-display text-[48px] font-medium leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] text-ink sm:text-[68px]">
    Philip Abao
  </h1>

  <div class="mt-10 grid gap-y-6 sm:mt-12 sm:grid-cols-[8.5rem_1fr] sm:gap-x-10">
    <figure class="m-0">
      <img
        src="/profile.jpg"
        alt="Philip Abao"
        width="120"
        height="120"
        onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/profile.svg'"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="h-20 w-20 rounded-sm object-cover ring-1 ring-rule-strong sm:ml-auto sm:h-[5.5rem] sm:w-[5.5rem]"
      />
    </figure>

    <div class="min-w-0">
      <p class="max-w-[56ch] font-serif text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-ink-2">
        At <span class="text-ink">Auxerta</span>, I'm building a post-transformer
        architecture with persistent memory and a new form of thought for AI.
        This site is the record: what I learn, what I break, what I make.
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="ml-1 whitespace-nowrap border-b border-accent-soft text-ink transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:text-accent"
        >More →</a>
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <Contact variant="row" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
